{
  "stem": "10406.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never, you know, when they said come, I didn't say no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put me in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the guy was an SS guy with a helmet and bayonet, driving into Chelm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm sitting on the-- you know, that extra seat, which was not smart because there were a lot of Polish Catholics there from my area.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I could have been-- I could have been recognized, except it would have blown their mind to say, what is he doing with the SS, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I found out now when I came back that they were worried about me being close to the-- with the Germans, because their house was, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was an underground cell of the Polish Underground.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they, they were a little bit-- they were suspicious of me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They thought maybe the Germans are using me to get information from them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't know that there was an underground cell there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked there for about a year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I slept in the same room with this one boy, whom I met recently in '93 when I was there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I always was careful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I watched myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somehow, one night, he spotted that I was circumcised.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he probably was confused because I used to go to confession.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to church.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he knew I was Catholic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was confusing to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He liked to drink.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So maybe one evening when he had some drinks, he may have told it to others as a fun thing that look, there's a Catholic here that's circumcised.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Imagine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how it happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the boys that I was pasturing the cows with were beginning to talk.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
